    "description": "<strong>Retro TV Game Collection is exactly that, a package of four time-honored classics from the dawn of home video games.</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823020/extras/c3aa295515403aaf7c921a84af82c89e.avif?t=1659472501\" width=650 height=64 /></span><br><br><strong>Tennis </strong><br>The one that started it all, known by many names, an instantly recognizable institution of gaming history.<br><br><strong>Football</strong><br>Licensed players and teams? of course not! better to see your friends fall to pieces as you score the last minute winner? Absolutely. <br><br><strong>Squash (Practice Mode)</strong><br>Tired of being humiliated by your friends or the CPU? Practice against nothing but the wall. Hone your reflexes and see how high you can score. <br><br><strong>Squash</strong><br>Put those practice sessions to the test, same wall, new opponent.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823020/extras/79a0216a0518ea9942a9b676d721b436.avif?t=1659472501\" width=650 height=64 /></span><br><br><strong>It may have taken 50 years but all games now feature these much needed improvements.</strong><br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Paddles no longer vanish off-screen!<br></li><li> Steam Remote Play!<br></li><li>CPU opponent means a new 1 player mode!<br></li><li>A score limit!<br></li><li> A pause button!<br></li><li> Full controller Support!<br></li><li> Stats!<br></li><li> Assist Mode!<br></li><li> Steam Cloud Saves!<br></li><li> Achievements!<br></li><li>Unlockables!<br></li><li>Co-op mode!</li></ul></strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823020/extras/0bc2d7566de201fc0083e5e79948f500.avif?t=1659472501\" width=650 height=64 /></span><br><br><strong>All updates will be FREE, FOREVER!!!!</strong><br>REALISTIC MODE - Sometimes quality of life updates are just not needed and only the original will do.<br>AFTER THAT - Let us know, anything else missing? something not quite right? Get in touch.<br><br><br>",
